data.description: This single-story 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch house is a fantastic opportunity located in the highly sought-after Kyrene School District. Situated on an oversized lot, this property offers ample space for your family's needs. Key features of this property include: 3 bedrooms, providing plenty of space for a growing family or guests. 2 bathrooms for added convenience and lots of storage. In 2021, new AC, new patio roof, new thermostat, smoke & carbon monoxide detectors were installed. No homeowners association (HOA), which means more flexibility and freedom in how you use and maintain your property. Patio has a misting system, low maintenance landscaping, and for the really warm days Nizomi aquatic center is minutes away. A prime location close to major employers and freeways 101, 202 &1 0
